  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dayasiri asks for more time",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliamentarian Mr. Dayasiri Jayasekara requested Deputy Speaker Mr. Ajith Rajapaksa to give more time to the forty-two MPs who were independent from the government to speak in Parliament.",
        "He mentioned that time should be allocated to his team by the government as well as the opposition.",
        "The chief organizer of the opposition, Mr. Lakshman Kiriella, has stated that since the independent group in the parliament is supporting the government's activities, it is not possible to give time from the opposition.",
        "He has further mentioned that the real opposition in the Parliament is Samagi Jana Balawega."
      ],
